name: Forest Jamban #020
description:
Far from massive civilization, there is massive forest live in the world. Animals and plants have live there for a thousand, or might be million years?

Then human there to live inside. They hunt animals, gathering plants and build small community called village.

Modernization have come and make people to left the forest for better opportunity and life. But what they build still remains here. Like the Jamban!

So much things changes, but forest still be important part of our lives. They provided oxygen, food, and place to live for animals and plants. So, we must protect it at whatever it cost!
